{"id":1734537,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:46:33.313Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1734537,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Inai Yang Hilang","overview":"# Translation  The story tells of a family celebrating the news that their eldest daughter, Sara, will marry her boyfriend, Wan Jamil. After the henna night, Sara seems anxious and wants to tell her younger sister, Ika, something. However, before she gets the chance to tell Ika, Sara and Wan Jamil disappear from home the next day. The house is in chaos as the family panics over the disappearance of the newlywed couple. From that day onwards, everyone becomes a suspect in the search for Sara and Wan Jamil. Razif's family blames Wan Jamil for intentionally eloping with Sara. Various speculations begin circulating on social media. Wan Jamil's wife, Noraini, is also under pressure as she begins receiving multiple threats. Razif becomes increasingly distressed over Sara's disappearance, and is comforted by Mimi. Razif seeks help from the public on his Instagram page and offers a cash reward.","popularity":0.0143,"poster_path":"/6u1P6rPYzjDPta226w4GApFUSKc.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2018-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Inai Yang Hilang","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1688486,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Kaka Azraff","original_name":"Kaka Azraff","popularity":0.3489,"profile_path":"/jJauLF5g8zKfnAyyf6FkQCRZM5s.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5e15d5e07f8633aaa4347c","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1752536,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Aishah Azman","original_name":"Aishah Azman","popularity":0.1309,"profile_path":null,"